  <brief_title>Femoral Remodeling Following Total Hip Arthroplasty With OMNI Apex Modular™ and OMNI Apex ARC™ Stem Compared to Competitive Designs</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Dual Energy X-Ray Absorptiometry (DXA) Evaluation Of Bone Density Changes After Hip Replacement. Performance Of The OMNI Apex Modular™ Hip Stem And The OMNI Apex ARC™ Hip Stem In Primary Total Hip Arthroplasty, Five-Year Clinical And DXA Analysis</official_title>
